annotationA: Microcephalin, isoform D; It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic nuclear division; pole cell formation; mushroom body development; embryo development
annotationB: Rad51C; Rad51 recombinase D (Rad51D) is a spn-A paralog involved in homologous recombination in the repair of double-strand breaks. Rad51D is likely important for regulating spn-A
